# Menu List

Camera menu options are listed below.

## Shooting Menus

Adjust settings when shooting photos or movies.

> ðŸ“„ See page 117 for details.

## Photo Menus

Items marked with both !Photo Icon and !Movie Icon icons are available in both the still photography and movie shooting menus. Changes to these items in either menu also apply to the item in the remaining menu.
